                <p><b>Internet or other electronic activity information</b>:<b> </b>your device or browser type and version; your browsing and search history on our Site; information on how you came to our Site; and information regarding your interactions with our Site and advertisements, including the dates and times of your visits, the pages you viewed, and the time spent on our Site</p>
